Symbol.Script_3D:
! Chair 09
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 THEN END
PEN gs_cont_pen
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
IF GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m=1
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 THEN RESOL 4 IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=2 THEN RESOL gs_resol
ADD a/2,b/2,0
unID=1 HOTSPOT -a/2, -b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a/2, -b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -a/2, b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a/2, b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
hotspot -a/2, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
hotspot a/2, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
mul a/0.5,b/0.45,zzyzx/0.44 ADD -0.2375, -0.2125, 0
MATERIAL gs_frame_mat
ADDZ 0.050 ROTY 180 ROTZ 180 GOSUB 1 GOSUB 1
! seat
ADD 0, -0.3875, -0.38
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL gs_seat_mat BLOCK 0.475, 0.350, 0.005
DEL TOP
END
1: ! half chrome bit ELBOW 0.0375, 90, 0.0125 ADD 0.0375, 0, 0.0375 ROTY 90 CYLIND 0.400, 0.0125 ADDZ 0.400 ELBOW 0.0375, 90, 0.0125 ADD 0.0375, 0, 0.0375 ROTY 90 CYLIND 0.340, 0.0125 ADDZ 0.340 ROTZ -90 ELBOW 0.0375, 90, 0.0125 ADD 0.0375, 0, 0.0375 ROTY 90 PEN gs_cont_pen SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND 0.350, 0.0125 ADDZ 0.350 PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ELBOW 0.0375, 90, 0.0125 ADD 0.0375, 0, 0.0375 ROTY 90 CYLIND 0.340, 0.0125 ADDZ 0.340 ROTZ 90
RETURN
Symbol.Script_2D:
! --- SCALE ---
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
! --- 2D SYMBOL ---
IF det2D = 1 THEN CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=3 !! 1/200 IF det2D = 2 THEN CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=3 !! 1/100 IF det2D = 4 THEN CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL !! Symbolic
IF gs_SymbolType_m=1 OR gs_SymbolType_m=2 THEN IF ABS(A-B) > EPS THEN HOTSPOT2 0,0 HOTSPOT2 A,0 HOTSPOT2 A,B HOTSPOT2 0,B ENDIF ENDIF
! --- 1/50 --- IF det2D = 3 THEN PEN gs_cont_pen
! Minimal Space and Hotspots
CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=0
ADD2 a/2,b/2
! Background Fill, Symbol mul2 a/0.5, b/0.45 ADD2 -0.2375, -0.2125
FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0.4875, 0.3875, 1, -0.0125, 0.3875, 1, -0.0125, 0.0375, 1, 0.4875, 0.0375, 1, 0.4875, 0.3875, -1
for i = 1 to 2 POLY2_B 8, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0.4375, 1, 0, 0.425, 900, 0, -90, 4001, 0.0125, 0.4125, 1, 0.4625, 0.4125, 1, 0.4625, 0.425, 1, 0.4750, 0.425, 900, 0, -90, 4001
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -0.0125, 0.3875, 1, 0.0125, 0.3875, 1, 0.0125, 0.425, 1, 0, 0.425, 900, 0, 180, 4001
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0.4625, 0.3875, 1, 0.4875, 0.3875, 1, 0.4875, 0.4250, 1, 0.4750, 0.4250, 900, 0, 180, 4001
add2 0,0.425 mul2 1, -1 next i del 4
del 3
ENDIF
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Chair 09 EPS=0.001
gs_OrigoCentered = 0
dim stSymbolTypes[16] stSymbolTypes[ 1] = `Круглый` stSymbolTypes[ 2] = `Круглый со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 3] = `Прямоугольный` stSymbolTypes[ 4] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` stSymbolTypes[ 5] = `Трапециевидный` stSymbolTypes[ 6] = `Трапециевидный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 7] = `Криволинейный` stSymbolTypes[ 8] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 9] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[10] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[11] = `Круглый со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[12] = `Круглый со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[13] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[14] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[15] = `Детальный 1` stSymbolTypes[16] = `Детальный 2`
Symbol.Script_VL:
HIDEPARAMETER ALL "A", "B", "zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0 values "gs_resol" range [3,) values "zzyzx" range [0.05, )
IF gs_cont_pen<=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen<=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, enable2dDetLevels = 2+4+8+16+32
if gs_detlevel_2D_m <> 4 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_SymbolType" lock "gs_SymbolType", "gs_SymbolType_m" endif
call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" THEN IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` THEN PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` ENDIF
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then lock "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" endif
! Minimal Space
VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSSide" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSRear" RANGE [0,)

ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
